data.description: Looking for a 4 Bedroom 2 1/2 Bath Affordable Home? Well Here it is! This OPEN CONCEPT Floor plan offers a Great Room and Dining with newer Plank Flooring and all Bedroom upstairs has newer Carpet as well. There is a cozy Kitchen freshly painted Cabinets, and Nice Tile Backsplash, Appliances all stay. The Master Bedroom offers a Master bath with Tub/Shower Combo as well as a Walk in closet. All 4 Bedrooms are very spacious. One of the Bedrooms features a Wall of Closet and Drawer space with Modern Cabinetry.  Outside you'll Find a Large Fenced Back yard. perfect for a secure play area for children and pets . The Oversized garage is an Added Plus.  And the Location...you'll find everything minutes away, Shopping, restaurants, YMCA, Schools, and of Course the Medical Complex's.  PLUS easy access to I-69.
